<title>AUSTRALIA: RTRS-Discovery shares up on Premier offer.</title>
<headline>RTRS-Discovery shares up on Premier offer.</headline>
<dateline>SYDNEY 1996-09-23</dateline>
<text>
<p>Shares in Australian oil producer Discovery Petroleum NL rose 21.7 percent after British oil group Premier Oil Plc announced a 70 cents a share takeover offer for the group earlier on Monday.</p>
<p>At 11.40 a.m. (0140 GMT), Discovery shares were 13 cents higher at 73 cents with 789,369 shares traded.</p>
<p>Premier bid values Discovery at about A$91.9 million.</p>
<p>-- Sydney newsroom 61-2 9373-1800</p>
</text>
